data.description: Spacious home with 4 to 5 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a 2 car garage on a corner lot! The main floor of this home has an eat-in kitchen, formal dining room, living room, bedroom, laundry and bathroom. Some of the original character includes two stained glass windows. Upstairs there are 4 bedrooms, office and bathroom. Garage is 2 car tandem.  The front porch is a great place to sit and enjoy the neighborhood.  The location is convenient to the Tamarack City and Lake Linden Parks.  Side yard has area for gardening and there are some raspberry plants and various flowers to enjoy. Fireplace: Pellet Stove in dining room.  Appliances: 2 Refrigerators. Water heater updated in 2020+/-, most windows replaced in 2001-2002+/-, porch updated in 2013+/-, furnace in 2008+/- and refrigerator in 2023.  NOTICE: All information believed accurate but not warranted. Buyer recommended to inspect all aspects of the property, verify all information & bears all risks for any inaccuracies. Tax information is subject to change (possibly significant) and property will be reassessed by the municipality after sale is completed. Owner has been exempt from property taxes, Buyer to obtain tax estimate from township assessor.  All measurements (acres, lot size, square footage etc) are estimated. Buyer to verify utilities, including availability & costs associated. Sellers may have audio/video recording devices present on property and buyers and agents consent to being recorded by entering property. OFFERS: Seller requests 72 hours response time on offers.  Seller, at seller's sole discretion, with or without notice, reserves the right to set and/or modify deadlines for receipt of and seller’s response to offers.
